Вакансія від 10 березня 2020
Customer Support Representative
Бит Системс
IT;
10–50 співробітників
Київ
Повна зайнятість, готові взяти студента.
Вища освіта.
Опис вакансії
Requirements:
Fluent in written and spoken English
Proficient PC and Internet user
Desire to work and learn
Sociability, analytical thinking
Acquaintance with online payments would be an advantage
Responsibilities:
Processing customers' support requests via email and chat
Watching online payment transactions flow
Investigating possible fraudulent payments
Work conditions:
Formal employment
Flexible working schedule
No night shifts
No calls
Paid vacation/sick days
Corporate events, great team and friendly atmosphere
